On Wednesday 9th September and Thursday 10th September, starting at 04:00 AEST

When they say 4:00 do they mean in the morning or afternoon
They mean AM, the way to tell is that they put a 0 before the 4. This implies AM in 24 hour time, because 4 pm is 16:00.  If it doesn't have a 4 digit time, they'll put an am/pm on it.
